      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   pos-cnf-ann-000      thru pos-cnf-ann-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Quindi si esce con Spaces               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-key-tus-ack          .
