           move      80                   to   v-car                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      01                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      all "-"              to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
