      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ON"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Uscita                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     pmt-key-reg-999.
       pmt-key-reg-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
