      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "OF"                 to   v-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                         using v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Erase linee impegnate                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "EL"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      04                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      07                   to   v-lto                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Data registrazione                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-dat-reg-000      thru pmt-dat-reg-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Tipo operazione                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-tip-ope-000      thru pmt-tip-ope-999        .
