      *                  * Numero distinta                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   pmt-num-dis-000      thru pmt-num-dis-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Linea di trattini                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
