           move      05                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      27                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-tes-tip-ope-des    to   v-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mvideo"
                                        using  v                      .
       vis-tip-ope-des-999.
